against 8,000 of us.

523
00:38:44,963 --> 00:38:46,521
You could have driven us
into the sea.

524
00:38:46,603 --> 00:38:49,071
If it weren't for your
German friends, we would have.

525
00:38:49,163 --> 00:38:52,201
My friends are the men
in my battery.

526
00:38:52,284 --> 00:38:55,161
People I grew up with.
People of my home town.

527
00:38:55,243 --> 00:38:57,917
So, what do you think
of our island, Captain?

528
00:38:58,004 --> 00:38:59,801
I like your island.

529
