and get a closer look.

555
00:41:23,254 --> 00:41:25,245
[Men laughing]

556
00:41:25,334 --> 00:41:26,687
We've met before.

557
00:41:26,774 --> 00:41:29,050
The surrender at the town hall.

558
00:41:29,135 --> 00:41:31,330
You are much better
at having parties...

559
00:41:31,414 --> 00:41:33,291
than you are
at negotiating surrender.

560
00:41:33,374 --> 00:41:34,887
Well, we're Italian.

561
00:41:34,975 --> 00:41:39,412
Famous for singing,
eating, making love.

562
00:41:39,495 --> 00:41:40,723
What's your name?

563
00:41:40,815 --> 00:41:43,410
Antonio Corelli. Grazie.

564
00:41:47,895 --> 00:41:50,330
Mmm. Mmm.

565
00:41:50,416 --> 00:41:53,010
You Germans always have
