had blond hair.

571
00:42:05,697 --> 00:42:06,846
I come from the Tyrol.

572
00:42:06,937 --> 00:42:09,132
Grew up
in the Austrian mountains.

573
00:42:09,217 --> 00:42:10,776
All my family,
and my family before them...

574
00:42:10,858 --> 00:42:13,816
