can remember, have dark hair.

575
00:42:13,898 --> 00:42:15,728
Like Adolf Hilter?

576
00:42:17,818 --> 00:42:20,378
You neglected
to tell me your rank.

577
00:42:20,458 --> 00:42:21,607
I am the breve.

578
00:42:21,698 --> 00:42:24,576
Maximilliano here
is the semibreve.

579
00:42:24,658 --> 00:42:25,933
He is the minim.

580
00:42:26,019 --> 00:42:28,010
Those boys are the crotchets
and the quavers.

581
00:42:28,099 --> 00:42:29,895
Piero here is the semiquaver.

582
00:42:29,978 --> 00:42:32,573
And Carlo is the rest.

583
00:42:32,659 --> 00:42:35,856
The pause between the notes.

584
00:42:35,939 --> 00:42:38,055
In the opera club, we have
our own ranking system...

585
00:42:38,139 --> 00:42:40,096
but otherwise I am a captain.

586
00:42:40,180 --> 00:42:42,455
33rd Regiment of Artillery.

587
00:42:42,540 --> 00:42:46,533
-Do you sing?
-Oh, no, uh, not really.

588
00:42:46,620 --> 00:42:49,088
Well, maybe, you know.

589
00:42:49,180 --> 00:42:51,740
On my own. In the bath.

590
00:42:51,820 --> 00:42:54,096
Well, have a drink. Be happy.

591
00:42:54,181 --> 00:42:55,409
But just remember...

592
00:42:55,501 --> 00:42:57,616
if you ever express
admiration for Wagner...

593
00:42:57,700 --> 00:43:00,453
you will be shot,
without trial...

594
00:43:00,540 --> 00:43:01,974
and without leave of appeal.

595
