664
00:48:59,246 --> 00:49:00,884
"Citizens of Cephallonia.

665
00:49:00,966 --> 00:49:03,560
"In these unfortunate
and difficult times...

666
00:49:03,646 --> 00:49:05,285
"Let us show the world...

667
00:49:05,367 --> 00:49:08,006
"how two ancient cultures
