673
00:50:00,730 --> 00:50:02,687
[Band playing waltz music]

674
00:50:14,251 --> 00:50:15,684
I'll be back in a moment.

675
00:50:28,812 --> 00:50:30,929
My friend thinks
you are very pretty.

676
00:50:31,013 --> 00:50:33,811
Why doesn't he tell me himself?

677
00:50:33,893 --> 00:50:35,564
He's too shy.

678
00:50:37,172 --> 00:50:40,324
He wants to know
