679
00:50:40,413 --> 00:50:43,405
No, I can't--
not with a German.

680
00:50:44,613 --> 00:50:46,844
But tell him thank you.

681
00:50:46,934 --> 00:50:49,731
Tell him I don't mean
to be rude.

682
00:50:54,374 --> 00:50:56,012
Uno momento.

683
00:51:06,815 --> 00:51:08,851
[New song starts]

684
00:52:10,780 --> 00:52:12,133
Don't stay up too late.

685
00:52:54,943 --> 00:52:56,978
