697
00:54:24,028 --> 00:54:26,224
and when the time comes...

698
00:54:26,309 --> 00:54:29,585
nobody must come down
to the beach.

699
00:54:29,669 --> 00:54:32,627
You must watch
from where you are.

700
00:55:34,753 --> 00:55:36,584
Capitano!

701
00:56:03,195 --> 00:56:07,712
You must be one of the most
stupid people I've ever met.

702
00:56:07,796 --> 00:56:11,027
You wanted to show off so
you nearly get us all killed.

703
00:56:11,116 --> 00:56:12,435
I can see your lips moving...

704
00:56:12,516 --> 00:56:14,030
but I can't hear
a word you're saying.

705
00:56:14,117 --> 00:56:16,506
It should pass--
in a day or two.

706
00:56:16,596 --> 00:56:19,156
Your father says
it will pass in a day or two.

707
00:56:19,236 --> 00:56:20,909
Does he?

708
00:56:20,997 --> 00:56:23,465
Is that what
the great doctor says?

709
00:56:23,557 --> 00:56:25,752
What are you saying?

710
00:56:25,837 --> 00:56:28,511
Are you saying
how beautiful life is...

711
00:56:28,598 --> 00:56:30,316
since the Italians arrived?

712
00:56:30,398 --> 00:56:32,353
All my life I've been waiting.

713
00:56:32,437 --> 00:56:35,077
I don't know
how I survived before you came.

714
00:56:35,158 --> 00:56:39,276
Are you saying how much
you missed having me around?

715
00:56:39,358 --> 00:56:41,668
I miss you so much
I can't sleep at night.

716
00:56:41,759 --> 00:56:43,192
The other night
when you were dancing...

717
00:56:43,279 --> 00:56:45,189
the way you were moving...

718
00:56:46,878 --> 00:56:49,632
The turn of your head.

719
00:56:49,719 --> 00:56:50,868
[Sighs]

720
00:56:50,959 --> 00:56:52,950
I thought
I could watch you forever.

721
00:56:55,039 --> 00:56:57,634
You think you can come here...

722
00:56:57,720 --> 00:57:01,507
and turn my whole world
upside-down?

723
