This is all I have.

726
00:57:10,481 --> 00:57:11,755
I can't give you any morphine.

727
00:57:11,841 --> 00:57:14,308
And we need
all the quinine we have.

728
00:57:14,400 --> 00:57:15,674
12,000 of our men
on the mainland...

729
00:57:15,760 --> 00:57:17,113
are sick with malaria.

730
00:57:17,200 --> 00:57:19,157
Supplies
are not getting through.

731
00:57:19,241 --> 00:57:21,550
Nobody knows why, nobody
knows what is happening...

732
00:57:21,641 --> 00:57:23,632
and I'm going to eat.

733
00:57:27,362 --> 00:57:31,400
You know,
when I met Pelagia's mother...

734
00:57:31,481 --> 00:57:35,521
she was betrothed
to somebody else.

735
00:57:35,602 --> 00:57:38,116
He nearly killed me.

736
00:57:38,202 --> 00:57:40,478
I had to leave the island.

737
00:57:40,563 --> 00:57:42,553
I had to lie low for a while.

738
00:57:45,843 --> 00:57:49,722
She wants to train
to be a doctor, you know.

739
00:57:49,803 --> 00:57:53,717
You think
she'd make a good doctor?

740
00:57:53,804 --> 00:57:56,238
I think she'd make
a very good doctor.

741
00:58:00,043 --> 00:58:02,035
IANNIS: Oh, uh...

742
00:58:04,884 --> 00:58:07,353
Another thing.

743
00:58:07,445 --> 00:58:11,198
This is a very ancient land...

744
00:58:11,284 --> 00:58:13,514
and we have had nothing
but earthquakes...

745
00:58:13,604 --> 00:58:16,073
and slaughter for 2,000 years.

746
00:58:16,165 --> 00:58:18,725
We've had massacres
at Sami and Fiskardo...

747
00:58:18,805 --> 00:58:21,444
and God knows where else.

748
00:58:21,526 --> 00:58:25,041
There will be more.

749
00:58:25,125 --> 00:58:28,880
It's only a question of time.

750
00:58:28,966 --> 00:58:31,400
So don't make any plans.

